name: in The Mood: Random Lines
description:
When I told her that she just sold one piece of screaming monster, she was so happy! 

Immediately wanted to make another one. We can be sure that purple is definitely her to go color these days. 
Yellow is a bit fading away. 


2100 x 2100
--
This project is a collaborative & learning platform between a tired mother and her (almost) 3 years old. Support our journey into NFT by collecting our creations or connect with us via Twitter. We'd love to make some new friends!
